<p>My team and I have been having a problem recently with our PathPlanner autos where the robot either won’t follow the path, or will follow the path and will start oscillating violently.  We’ve had some theories on why it has been doing this such as the rotation and translation PIDs, but even after testing those values, the robot still does not follow the path.  Could one of you guys please take a look at the auto code and the repo linked below.  It would be of great help if you guys can help us solve this issue.</p>
<p><strong>Drivetrain AutoBuilder:</strong></p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">   public void AutoBuilder() {
        System.out.println("AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA");
